title: Match of the Day - FA Cup First Round Highlights 08.11.2015 SD
description:
Match of the Day - FA Cup First Round Highlights 08.11.2015 SD

Highlights from the FA Cup first round. Non-league sides that have battled through the preliminary rounds will be looking to extend their cup runs and make a name for themselves, while the 48 League One and Two clubs that enter at this stage will be aiming to avoid any embarrassing slip-ups while harbouring their own dreams of cup glory. Last season, Warrington Town and Worcester City made the headlines at this stage with wins against Exeter City and Coventry City
